snippet.title: Monster Meals - Official Release Date Revealed!
snippet.description:
Get ready! Monster Meals officially launches on January 17th! 🎉
Join the fun in this monster-filled cooking game where you must serve dishes before they lose their patience… or you might be on the menu! 😱

🎮 Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3021850/Monster_Meals/
👾 Follow us for more updates and exclusive content!
